就嚟滿瀉就嗱嗱淋走出廁格 洗手嗰陣聽到啲屎水瀉咗出嚟 <br />\n<br />\n仲要隔離廁格條友我識<br />\n佢應該心諗做乜會有水流過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8450ec9ea1b2c08873a1fcf4f67aba85a915223","tid":746233,"uid":49816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"試過去希慎個廁所沖左7次先沖得走舊屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出面仲好多人排緊"},{"pid":"8ce23728fc36979415216ec0f5e777582a389fd1","tid":746233,"uid":39573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"拎張紙巾擋住咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feaa9801807aec47d3e234576c3ba5f32b33fdc0","tid":746233,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"其實點解香港唔用日本個d沖屎眼暖板廁所<br />\n真心好用 <br />\n人地平民化科技 照計應該唔貴<br />\n感覺又高級d <br />\n就算屋企無 大型商場點解唔引入<br />\n韓國台灣都見到有"},{"pid":"098f24ec54e1f4d96a006ccb2ebc9459e022c282","tid":746233,"uid":1221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"你感覺得係個設計問題定係有其他&quot;野&quot;幫你沖廁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258b72ebee3046a09826ca6ea214ec2d04ea291d","tid":746233,"uid":38030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"企喺身㧾屎，㧾完又要等佢儲夠水先可以沖多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff0e83c7044c1759139c0e7844e29e151886016","tid":746233,"uid":22789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T14:12:19.000Z","msg":"我都好撚憎依種感應沖廁 次次去完都要講粗口<br />\n係又沖唔係又沖 鋪好晒紙巾準備坐落去痾又沖<br />\n痾痾下又沖 最嘔心係d廁所水彈到下面<br />\n大佬 廁所水乜菌都有 是但中一樣都仆街啦"},{"pid":"0e961a81147e59425a65fa7cd491e4a8745eb513